#

Bourbon-Glazed Salmon with Asparagus and Wild Rice Pilaf

$25.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carbohydrate

Tags:

GourmetHealthyMain Course

Description

A sweet and savory bourbon glaze elevates tender salmon, paired with crisp asparagus and a nutty wild rice pilaf for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 (6 oz each)
  • Bourbon: 1/4 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Asparagus (trimmed): 1 pound
  • Wild rice blend: 1 cup
  • Chicken broth: 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Lemon wedges: for serving
